OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for SUN 31 MAY
OL,4,G2200F1971: The Year We Went Decimal
OL,5,     GWelcome to the wonderful story of
OL,6,     Gthe decimalisation of British
OL,7,     Gcurrency in 1971 - the biggest
OL,8,     Gchange in UK monetary history -
OL,9,     Gwhen pounds, shillings and pence
OL,10,     Gwere replaced.
OL,11,G2300FTaggart
OL,12,     GWhat became of The Adders, a
OL,13,     Glegendary Scottish pop group of
OL,14,     Gthe sixties? A deadly plot is
OL,15,     Gthwarting any hope of a reunion
OL,16,     Gas the Taggart team face a race
OL,17,     Gagainst time.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
